FieldReferenceFilter

public FieldReferenceFilter(boolean include,
                            Set<String> referenceObjectNames)
Initializes an FieldReferenceFilter with a set of Force.com schema object names. Any reference field to one of these object will be filtered.

Parameters:
include - whether this FieldReferenceFilter is an include filter or exclude filter
referenceObjectNames - a java.util.Set of exact object names that are to be filtered in

FieldReferenceFilter

public FieldReferenceFilter(boolean include,
                            String... referenceObjectNames)
Initializes an FieldReferenceFilter with a set of Force.com schema object names. Any reference field to one of these object will be filtered.

Note that duplicates within the given array will be eliminated.

Parameters:
include - whether this FieldReferenceFilter is an include filter or exclude filter
referenceObjectNames - an Array of exact object names that are to be filtered
